<subSubSection id="C31343D2FFC8FFAD6180FC05C163FBB0" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB61059FFC8FFAD6180FC05C163FBB0" blockId="4.[151,1436,870,1077]" pageId="4" pageNumber="305">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC8FFAD6180FC05C460FC68" bold="true" box="[199,315,979,1005]" pageId="4" pageNumber="305">Remarks.</emphasis>
Present species is related to ‘ 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC8FFAD63C1FC05C6D5FC68" baseAuthorityName="Lohmann" baseAuthorityYear="1893" box="[646,910,979,1005]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulcher">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC8FFAD63C1FC05C6D5FC68" box="[646,910,979,1005]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="305">Copidognathus pulcher</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ group (
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC8FFAD62ACFC05C1CAFC68" author="Bartsch, I." box="[1003,1169,979,1005]" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" pagination="27 - 31" refId="ref8320" refString="Bartsch, I. (1984 a) Two new species of the pulcher group in the genus Copidognathus (Acari, Halacaridae). Zoologica Scripta, 13, 27 - 31. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1463 - 6409.1984. tb 00019. x" type="journal article" year="1984">Bartsch 1984a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC8FFAD65DAFC05C58AFB94" author="Chatterjee, T. &amp; De Troch, M." pageId="4" pageNumber="305" pagination="177 - 194" refId="ref11089" refString="Chatterjee, T. &amp; De Troch, M. (2000) Halacaridae (Acari) from Gazi Bay (Kenya): description and biogeography of three new and two known species. Hydrobiologia, 427, 177 - 194. https: // doi. org / 10.1023 / A: 1003979629889" type="journal article" year="2000">Chatterjee &amp; De Troch 2000</bibRefCitation>
) but the nature of porose panels on anterior areolae of AD and the setal ornamentation of legs were different between the members of 
<taxonomicName id="4C096BDAFFC8FFAD60F6FBCDC77CFBB0" baseAuthorityName="Lohmann" baseAuthorityYear="1893" box="[433,551,1051,1077]" class="Arachnida" family="Halacaridae" genus="Copidognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulcher">
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC8FFAD60F6FBCDC77CFBB0" box="[433,551,1051,1077]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="305">C. pulcher</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group and this species (Chatterjee 
<emphasis id="B97DCC4BFFC8FFAD62F7FBCDC6BAFBB0" box="[944,993,1051,1077]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="305">et al</emphasis>
. 2003).
</paragraph>
